This c++11 code sample completes my blog article at:

 - http://www.kakesa.net/programmation/cplusplus11-decouverte-de-ce-nouveau-dialecte/797
 - http://www.kakesa.net/programmation/cplusplus11-les-expressions-lambda/861

This code is tested on Ubuntu GNU/Linux 13.04 with clanb++ and libc++ : http://www.kakesa.net/projets-perso/installer-libc-sur-ubuntu-13-04-x86_64/1241.

Build the code in "build/bin" directory by typing :

  make

Make a tar archive in "build" directory by typing :

  make tar
